{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":408,"text":"So imagine that a plane is about to crash"},{"time":6170,"text":"with 250 children and babies,"},{"time":8971,"text":"and if you knew how to stop that, would you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":12390,"text":"Now imagine"},{"time":14361,"text":"that 60 planes full of babies under five"},{"time":18000,"text":"crash every single day."},{"time":21210,"text":"That's the number of kids"},{"time":22982,"text":"that never make it to their fifth birthday."},{"time":25307,"text":"6.6 million children"},{"time":28547,"text":"never make it to their fifth birthday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32138,"text":"Most of these deaths are preventable,"},{"time":34594,"text":"and that doesn't just make me sad,"},{"time":36562,"text":"it makes me angry,"},{"time":38258,"text":"and it makes me determined."},{"time":40616,"text":"Diarrhea and pneumonia"},{"time":42506,"text":"are among the top two killers"},{"time":44322,"text":"of children under five,"},{"time":46640,"text":"and what we can do to prevent these diseases"},{"time":48896,"text":"isn't some smart,"},{"time":51076,"text":"new technological innovations."},{"time":53993,"text":"It's one of the world's oldest inventions:"},{"time":58872,"text":"a bar of soap."},{"time":62397,"text":"Washing hands with soap,"},{"time":63829,"text":"a habit we all take for granted,"},{"time":66200,"text":"can reduce diarrhea by half,"},{"time":68484,"text":"can reduce respiratory infections by one third."},{"time":72140,"text":"Handwashing with soap"},{"time":73911,"text":"can have an impact"},{"time":75560,"text":"on reducing flu, trachoma, SARS,"},{"time":80587,"text":"and most recently in the case of cholera"},{"time":82977,"text":"and Ebola outbreak,"},{"time":85667,"text":"one of the key interventions"},{"time":87358,"text":"is handwashing with soap."},{"time":90176,"text":"Handwashing with soap keeps kids in school."},{"time":93431,"text":"It stops babies from dying."},{"time":96254,"text":"Handwashing with soap"},{"time":98127,"text":"is one of the most cost-effective"},{"time":100924,"text":"ways of saving children's lives."},{"time":103470,"text":"It can save over 600,000 children every year."},{"time":107126,"text":"That's the equivalent of stopping"},{"time":110090,"text":"10 jumbo jets"},{"time":112070,"text":"full of babies and children"},{"time":113998,"text":"from crashing every single day."},{"time":116709,"text":"I think you'll agree with me that that's a pretty"},{"time":119133,"text":"useful public health intervention."}]},{"cues":[{"time":122415,"text":"So now just take a minute."},{"time":125365,"text":"I think you need to get to\nknow the person next to you."},{"time":127301,"text":"Why don't you just shake their hands."},{"time":129249,"text":"Please shake their hands."},{"time":131493,"text":"All right, get to know each other."},{"time":132793,"text":"They look really pretty."},{"time":134328,"text":"All right."},{"time":136101,"text":"So what if I told you"},{"time":138399,"text":"that the person whose hands you just shook"},{"time":140984,"text":"actually didn't wash their hands"},{"time":142692,"text":"when they were coming out of the toilet?\n(Laughter)"},{"time":145350,"text":"They don't look so pretty anymore, right?"},{"time":148680,"text":"Pretty yucky, you would agree with me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151836,"text":"Well, statistics are actually showing"},{"time":153501,"text":"that four people out of five"},{"time":155917,"text":"don't wash their hands when\nthey come out of the toilet,"},{"time":158525,"text":"globally."},{"time":160213,"text":"And the same way,"},{"time":162483,"text":"we don't do it when we've got fancy toilets,"},{"time":165227,"text":"running water, and soap available,"},{"time":167677,"text":"it's the same thing in the countries"},{"time":169611,"text":"where child mortality is really high."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172985,"text":"What is it? Is there no soap?"},{"time":175299,"text":"Actually, soap is available."},{"time":177548,"text":"In 90 percent of households in India,"},{"time":181203,"text":"94 percent of households in Kenya,"},{"time":183883,"text":"you will find soap."},{"time":185363,"text":"Even in countries where soap is the lowest,"},{"time":189200,"text":"like Ethiopia, we are at 50 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192779,"text":"So why is it?"},{"time":194006,"text":"Why aren't people washing their hands?"},{"time":196939,"text":"Why is it that Mayank,"},{"time":199323,"text":"this young boy that I met in India,"},{"time":201590,"text":"isn't washing his hands?"},{"time":203335,"text":"Well, in Mayank's family,"},{"time":205947,"text":"soap is used for bathing,"},{"time":208379,"text":"soap is used for laundry,"},{"time":210371,"text":"soap is used for washing dishes."},{"time":213240,"text":"His parents think sometimes"},{"time":215107,"text":"it's a precious commodity,"},{"time":216671,"text":"so they'll keep it in a cupboard."},{"time":218938,"text":"They'll keep it away from him so he doesn't waste it."},{"time":221692,"text":"On average, in Mayank's family,"},{"time":224242,"text":"they will use soap for washing hands"},{"time":226314,"text":"once a day"},{"time":227765,"text":"at the very best, and sometimes"},{"time":230130,"text":"even once a week for washing hands with soap."},{"time":233115,"text":"What's the result of that?"},{"time":235330,"text":"Children pick up disease"},{"time":237195,"text":"in the place that's supposed to love them"},{"time":238870,"text":"and protect them the most, in their homes."}]},{"cues":[{"time":243778,"text":"Think about where you learned to wash your hands."},{"time":246326,"text":"Did you learn to wash your hands at home?"},{"time":249130,"text":"Did you learn to wash your hands in school?"},{"time":251906,"text":"I think behavioral scientists will tell you"},{"time":254386,"text":"that it's very difficult to change the habits"},{"time":256925,"text":"that you have had early in life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261810,"text":"However, we all copy what everyone else does,"},{"time":264607,"text":"and local cultural norms are something"},{"time":267331,"text":"that shape how we change our behavior,"},{"time":270642,"text":"and this is where the private sector comes in."},{"time":273418,"text":"Every second in Asia and Africa,"},{"time":277218,"text":"111 mothers"},{"time":280140,"text":"will buy this bar to protect their family."},{"time":283858,"text":"Many women in India will tell you"},{"time":285898,"text":"they learned all about hygiene, diseases,"},{"time":288124,"text":"from this bar of soap from Lifebuoy brand."},{"time":291870,"text":"Iconic brands like this one"},{"time":293745,"text":"have a responsibility to do good"},{"time":295633,"text":"in the places where they sell their products."},{"time":298114,"text":"It's that belief, plus the scale of Unilever,"},{"time":301289,"text":"that allows us to keep talking about"},{"time":303729,"text":"handwashing with soap and\nhygiene to these mothers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307545,"text":"Big businesses and brands can change"},{"time":310817,"text":"and shift those social norms"},{"time":312969,"text":"and make a difference for those habits"},{"time":314881,"text":"that are so stubborn."},{"time":317061,"text":"Think about it:"},{"time":318319,"text":"Marketeers spend all their time"},{"time":321824,"text":"making us switch from one brand to the other."},{"time":326180,"text":"And actually, they know how to transform"},{"time":329170,"text":"science and facts into compelling messages."},{"time":332203,"text":"Just for a minute, imagine"},{"time":334099,"text":"when they put all their forces behind"},{"time":336840,"text":"a message as powerful as handwashing with soap."},{"time":339790,"text":"The profit motive is transforming health outcomes"},{"time":342749,"text":"in this world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":344627,"text":"But it's been happening for centuries:"},{"time":346446,"text":"the Lifebuoy brand was launched in 1894"},{"time":349979,"text":"in Victorian England"},{"time":351715,"text":"to actually combat cholera."},{"time":353987,"text":"Last week, I was in Ghana"},{"time":356291,"text":"with the minister of health,"},{"time":357830,"text":"because if you don't know,"},{"time":359049,"text":"there's a cholera outbreak in Ghana at the moment."},{"time":361706,"text":"A hundred and eighteen years later,"},{"time":363842,"text":"the solution is exactly the same:"},{"time":365762,"text":"It's about ensuring that they have access"},{"time":368258,"text":"to this bar of soap,"},{"time":369674,"text":"and that they're using it,"},{"time":371419,"text":"because that's the number one way"},{"time":373379,"text":"to actually stop cholera from spreading."},{"time":376610,"text":"I think this drive for profit"},{"time":379010,"text":"is extremely powerful,"},{"time":380881,"text":"sometimes more powerful than"},{"time":382341,"text":"the most committed charity or government."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385636,"text":"Government is doing what they can,"},{"time":387438,"text":"especially in terms of the pandemics"},{"time":390813,"text":"and epidemics such as cholera,"},{"time":393350,"text":"or Ebola at the moment,"},{"time":394805,"text":"but with competing priorities."},{"time":397345,"text":"The budget is not always there."},{"time":399850,"text":"And when you think about this,"},{"time":401713,"text":"you think about what is required"},{"time":403820,"text":"to make handwashing a daily habit,"},{"time":406141,"text":"it requires sustained funding"},{"time":409962,"text":"to refine this behavior."},{"time":413070,"text":"In short, those that fight for public health"},{"time":417503,"text":"are actually dependent upon the soap companies"},{"time":420267,"text":"to keep promoting handwashing with soap."},{"time":423263,"text":"We have friends like USAID,"},{"time":426505,"text":"the Global Public-Private Partnership\nfor Handwashing with Soap,"},{"time":429810,"text":"London School of Hygiene and Tropical Medicine,"},{"time":431970,"text":"Plan, WaterAid,"},{"time":433539,"text":"that all believe"},{"time":435046,"text":"for a win-win-win partnership."},{"time":438761,"text":"Win for the public sector,"},{"time":440746,"text":"because we help them reach their targets."},{"time":443821,"text":"Win for the private sector,"},{"time":446209,"text":"because we build new generations"},{"time":447623,"text":"of future handwashers."},{"time":449420,"text":"And most importantly,"},{"time":451633,"text":"win for the most vulnerable."},{"time":454240,"text":"On October 15,"},{"time":456296,"text":"we will celebrate Global Handwashing Day."},{"time":458648,"text":"Schools, communities,"},{"time":460368,"text":"our friends in the public sector"},{"time":462248,"text":"and our friends in the private sector —"},{"time":464864,"text":"yes, on that day even our competitors,"},{"time":467144,"text":"we all join hands to celebrate"},{"time":469130,"text":"the world's most important"},{"time":471112,"text":"public health intervention."},{"time":473160,"text":"What's required,"},{"time":474385,"text":"and again where the private sector\ncan make a huge difference,"},{"time":477121,"text":"is coming up with this big, creative thinking"},{"time":480887,"text":"that drives advocacy."},{"time":483128,"text":"If you take our Help a Child Reach 5 campaign,"},{"time":485791,"text":"we've created great films"},{"time":488770,"text":"that bring the message of handwashing with soap"},{"time":490856,"text":"to the everyday person"},{"time":492551,"text":"in a way that can relate to them."},{"time":495127,"text":"We've had over 30 million views."},{"time":496887,"text":"Most of these discussions are still happening online."},{"time":499414,"text":"I urge you to take five minutes"},{"time":500886,"text":"and look at those films."}]},{"cues":[{"time":504943,"text":"I come from Mali,"},{"time":506472,"text":"one of the world's poorest countries."},{"time":508815,"text":"I grew up in a family where every dinner conversation"},{"time":511551,"text":"was around social justice."},{"time":513729,"text":"I trained in Europe's premier school of public health."},{"time":517257,"text":"I think I'm probably one of the only women"},{"time":518985,"text":"in my country with this high degree in health,"},{"time":522426,"text":"and the only one"},{"time":523910,"text":"with a doctorate in handwashing with soap."},{"time":527512,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":529248,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":535872,"text":"Nine years ago, I decided,"},{"time":538223,"text":"with a successful public health career in the making,"},{"time":541136,"text":"that I could make the biggest impact coming,"},{"time":544664,"text":"selling and promoting the world's best invention"},{"time":547695,"text":"in public health: soap."},{"time":550230,"text":"We run today the world's largest"},{"time":552359,"text":"handwashing program"},{"time":553730,"text":"by any public health standards."},{"time":556308,"text":"We've reached over 183 million people"},{"time":559780,"text":"in 16 countries."},{"time":562970,"text":"My team and I have the ambition"},{"time":564806,"text":"to reach one billion by 2020."},{"time":568564,"text":"Over the last four years,"},{"time":570758,"text":"business has grown double digits,"},{"time":573486,"text":"whilst child mortality has reduced"},{"time":575423,"text":"in all the places where soap use has increased."},{"time":579845,"text":"It may be uncomfortable for some to hear —"},{"time":582150,"text":"business growth and lives saved"},{"time":584405,"text":"somehow equated in the same sentence —"},{"time":587918,"text":"but it is that business growth"},{"time":589837,"text":"that allows us to keep doing more."},{"time":592133,"text":"Without it, and without talking about it,"},{"time":594877,"text":"we cannot achieve the change that we need."}]},{"cues":[{"time":598925,"text":"Last week, my team and I"},{"time":601110,"text":"spent time visiting mothers"},{"time":604406,"text":"that have all experienced the same thing:"},{"time":606917,"text":"the death of a newborn."},{"time":609349,"text":"I'm a mom. I can't imagine anything more powerful"},{"time":612349,"text":"and more painful."},{"time":615262,"text":"This one is from Myanmar."},{"time":617894,"text":"She had the most beautiful smile,"},{"time":619900,"text":"the smile, I think, that life gives you"},{"time":622110,"text":"when you've had a second chance."},{"time":624497,"text":"Her son, Myo, is her second one."},{"time":627831,"text":"She had a daughter"},{"time":629735,"text":"who passed away at three weeks,"},{"time":632127,"text":"and we know that the majority"},{"time":634480,"text":"of children that actually die"},{"time":635820,"text":"die in the first month of their life,"},{"time":637686,"text":"and we know that if we give a bar of soap"},{"time":640554,"text":"to every skilled birth attendant,"},{"time":642814,"text":"and that if soap is used \nbefore touching the babies,"},{"time":645364,"text":"we can reduce and make a change"},{"time":646606,"text":"in terms of those numbers."},{"time":648650,"text":"And that's what inspires me,"},{"time":650518,"text":"inspires me to continue in this mission,"},{"time":652750,"text":"to know that I can equip her"},{"time":655134,"text":"with what's needed"},{"time":656939,"text":"so that she can do"},{"time":658790,"text":"the most beautiful job in the world:"},{"time":660854,"text":"nurturing her newborn."},{"time":662980,"text":"And next time you think of a gift"},{"time":665285,"text":"for a new mom and her family,"},{"time":667375,"text":"don't look far: buy her soap."},{"time":670165,"text":"It's the most beautiful invention in public health."}]},{"cues":[{"time":673373,"text":"I hope you will join us"},{"time":675749,"text":"and make handwashing part of your daily lives"},{"time":678701,"text":"and our daily lives"},{"time":680405,"text":"and help more children like Myo"},{"time":682629,"text":"reach their fifth birthday."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683757,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686164,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}